<figureCitation id="4EC91DF71FD5DD5903CAD7AD7BAFB382" captionStart="Figure 47" captionStartId="F47" captionText="Figure 47. Map of geographic distribution of L. grandifolia based on herbarium specimen data." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.168.51904.figure47" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/480059" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">47</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
